track_notes: Classification EE. From Italian side 8 km . Long but easy path to the col Acles. After you must search your right path between stones on a slippery slope. From the pass des Rousses easy ridge to the summit. For the back-way we go down from the steep and slipper north side of Rousses saving Km but not ankles and knees.

From Pamplinet, private way (and no 4x4 ;-) ) Take Care during the last ascend... I prefer past by the rock... But going down my package get down down down don t follow my trace step by step ! Stay Safe !
